entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You found Vryim Raeth, but it was too late. He was alreadyt dead.
entries.journal_entry_description: Vryim Raeth disappeared a few weeks ago. His wife, Cara, believes the Chirq Council took him because they thought he knew too much about their operations. She wants you to find Vryim for her.
entries.task00_item_name: You found the corpse of Vryim Raeth
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Vryim Reath is believed to be a captive of the Chirq Council. Find him.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Cara Raeth with the bad news about her husband. At least she will now be able to properly mourn him.
